726
01:12:42,000 --> 01:12:42,800
Obejmeš mě?

727
01:13:12,490 --> 01:13:13,190
Sbohem.

728
01:13:49,920 --> 01:13:51,870
Chiyako má dobrý vkus.

729
01:13:52,450 --> 01:13:53,940
Tohle je super roztomilé.

730
01:13:57,730 --> 01:13:58,690
Jak?

731
01:14:01,310 --> 01:14:03,830
